to me twice.

11:13.800 --> 11:17.867
-I'm so sorry.
-Jessica, what's in that car?

11:17.900 --> 11:20.200
-That's it.
-What else is in that car?

11:20.233 --> 11:22.833
-That's it, I swear.
-Well, you told me
that was it last time.

11:22.867 --> 11:25.233
-I swear to God.

11:25.267 --> 11:27.467
I'm telling the truth,
that's it.
-Are there drugs in that car?

11:27.500 --> 11:30.067
-No. Please-- Please
search the car.

11:30.067 --> 11:33.267
-Well, I have-- have
to get consent from him,
so, sit tight.

11:35.867 --> 11:39.867
She had
another pipe on her.
A second one.

11:39.900 --> 11:43.267
Okay, so, here's the deal.
Your girlfriend drops a pipe,
and then she gives me

11:43.300 --> 11:45.600
another pipe in the back seat
of my partner's car over here.

11:45.633 --> 11:48.400
And then you deny consent.
And I don't wanna violate
your rights, I'm not tryin'

11:48.433 --> 11:51.167
to do that.
But I think there's something
in the car

11:51.200 --> 11:52.900
that you don't want me
to find.
-There ain't nothing.

11:52.933 --> 11:54.367
We-- That's it,
right there.

11:54.400 --> 11:56.367
-I-- I don't--
-I will admit we did
smoke a little bit.

11:56.400 --> 11:59.500
What we smoked,
it was about a bowl or two,
and we smoked it all.

11:59.533 --> 12:02.733
There ain't nothin'.
-If there's nothin' in the car,
then why are you

12:02.767 --> 12:05.600
bein' suspicious about it?
-Because, this is my
personal effects, and it's

12:05.633 --> 12:08.167
where I live.
-And I understand that.
I'm just tryin' to make sure

12:08.200 --> 12:10.667
that there's no drugs
in my neighborhood
where I-- where I'm working.

12:10.700 --> 12:13.300
-And there ain't anymore.
